  <brief_title>&quot;Early TIPS&quot; Versus Glue Obliteration to Prevent Rebleeding From Gastric Varices</brief_title>
  <acronym>GAVAPROSEC</acronym>
  <official_title>A Multicenter Randomized Clinical Trial Comparing Two Treatment Strategies to Prevent Rebleeding From Gastric Varices: &quot;Early TIPS&quot; Versus Glue Obliteration</official_title>
